## How to Use This Template

This is an example blog post showing how to integrate Gamma presentations into your blog.

To create your own Gamma presentation post:

1. **Get your Gamma presentation ID:**
   - Open your presentation in Gamma
   - Click the Share button
   - Look for the embed code or share URL
   - Extract the presentation ID from the URL (the part after `/docs/` or `/embed/`)

2. **Update the frontmatter:**
   - Replace `REPLACE-WITH-YOUR-GAMMA-ID` with your actual Gamma presentation ID
   - Update the title, excerpt, category, and tags
   - Set `source: "gamma"` and `presentationType: "gamma"`

3. **Optional: Add supporting content:**
   - You can add additional markdown content below to provide context
   - The presentation will render first, followed by any markdown content

The presentation will automatically embed above this content with a responsive 16:9 aspect ratio.

