```

## Features

- **Responsive Design:** Presentations automatically adapt to screen sizes
- **Loading State:** Shows a loading indicator while the presentation loads
- **Visual Badge:** Posts with presentations display a presentation badge on the blog list
- **Standalone or Hybrid:** Use presentations alone or combine with markdown content
- **SEO Friendly:** All metadata (title, excerpt, tags) are indexed for search
